data.title: ella fitzgerald
data.meta_description: many famous people are buried at Inglewood Cemetery. after i visited the graves of my ancestors, i visited the resting place of the great Ella Fitzgerald. i've long been a great fan of this great jazz vocalist. it was only fitting that i stop by to say "hello" since i was in the neighborhood. via Instagram www.instagram.com/p/BKjQd9DDDFD/
data.text:
many famous people are buried at Inglewood Cemetery. after i visited the graves of my ancestors, i visited the resting place of the great Ella Fitzgerald. i've long been a great fan of this great jazz vocalist. it was only fitting that i stop by to say "hello" since i was in the neighborhood.

via Instagram www.instagram.com/p/BKjQd9DDDFD/
